<BlogLayout
  title="GTS Meaning in Text — Go To Sleep or Good Times?"
  description="GTS in text means 'Go To Sleep' (telling someone to rest) or 'Good Times' (celebrating a fun moment). Learn which meaning applies and see real examples."
  canonical="/blog/gts-meaning-in-text"
  date="2026-06-23"
